TRICEP MASS WORKOUT (no equipment needed) -

#1 Tiger push-up is the most intense workout which helps you feel a lot of tricep and also part of body control. Core is your secondary can be train in this form. 10reps/12reps/15repsX3sets/4sets

#2 As for beginner, you should try on your knees first for Tiger push-up and there you will get to observe the motions and you'll get to the point let the body do the work till you can move on through without the knees on the ground anymore.

#Additional - You can try called Tricep extension which means find any barbell objects which is near  almost the bottom as in smith machine, squat rack or anywhere anything which sees more convenient for you. Next thing you gonna do it like how you did the tiger push-up. Benefits is can be train to your tricep is primary and to your chest is your secondary. 12/15repsX3sets/4sets

Have a try this badass workout and let me know the feedback! Thanks!
